com.yworks.yfiles.graph

Class FoldingEdgeState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.FoldingLabelOwnerState
      • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.FoldingEdgeState

  • public final class FoldingEdgeState
extends FoldingLabelOwnerState
    A data container representing the state of an edge whose source and/or target node are collapsed.

    When the properties of the state are changed, these changes are reflected immediately in the Views.

    See Also:
    FoldingEdgeStateId, FoldingManager.getFoldingEdgeState(FoldingEdgeStateId)

        Parameters:
        location - The location of the new bend state.
        index - The index the bend state shall be inserted in the Bends; a negative value (which is the default) indicates that the bend should be appended to the end of the list of bends.

      • asEdge

        public final IEdge asEdge()
        Returns an IEdge instance which represents this edge state.

        The returned edge is not present in any graph but may be passed to IFoldingView.getViewItem(com.yworks.yfiles.graph.IModelItem) to get the edge state's view edge in the folding view graph.

        Returns:
        An IEdge instance which represents this edge state.
